a victim of sex trafficking.

125
00:05:20,407 --> 00:05:22,626
So we start with
what was left behind.

126
00:05:22,670 --> 00:05:24,802
I want every piece of paper
on that apartment...

127
00:05:24,846 --> 00:05:26,935
