every in-service call.

128
00:05:26,978 --> 00:05:30,460
Just scour that crime scene.
Work the bodies.

129
00:05:30,504 --> 00:05:32,636
Find out what the hell happened
in that apartment.

130
00:05:36,118 --> 00:05:37,902
We've been working
round the clock.

131
00:05:37,946 --> 00:05:40,862
