from Cleveland.

178
00:07:12,693 --> 00:07:15,059
I ran those coordinates
for John Doe's bullet wounds,

179
00:07:15,100 --> 00:07:16,566
for the finger injury.

180
00:07:16,610 --> 00:07:18,438
Got a hit.

181
00:07:27,534 --> 00:07:29,579
Edgar Torres.

182
00:07:31,973 --> 00:07:34,105
